{"sgc":false,"sfy":false,"qfy":false,"transUser":{"id":4048938,"status":99,"demand":1,"userid":0,"nickname":"鸽子话","uptime":1557488390560},"lyricUser":{"id":4048935,"status":99,"demand":0,"userid":48965375,"nickname":"Feliciayang","uptime":1557488390560},"lrc":{"version":23,"lyric":"{\"t\":0,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作词: \"},{\"tx\":\"Phoebe Ryan\"}]}\n{\"t\":1000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"ILLENIUM\"}]}\n{\"t\":2000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"编曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"ILLENIUM\"}]}\n[00:21.300]When it went down\n[00:23.570]It was so hard to breathe\n[00:26.280]I gave up everything\n[00:28.700]In the slow fall down to the floor\n[00:33.420]Life was escaping me\n[00:35.760]I couldn’t find myself\n[00:38.200]Till it was all lost\n[00:40.860]Not anymore\n[00:42.740]I’m holding on to all the pieces of my heart’s debris\n[00:47.670]Till it’s time\n[00:50.670]I’ll… I’ll pull it together and fix myself eventually\n[00:57.200]I know it’s mine\n[00:59.720]I found gold in the wreckage\n[01:01.920]Put it on a necklace\n[01:04.320]Keepin’ it cause I-I-I, I know that it’s mine\n[01:09.100]I wear it like a message\n[01:11.670]So I don’t forget it\n[01:14.140]Keepin’ it cause I-I-I, I know that it’s mine\n[01:19.700]I know that it's mine\n[01:24.480]I know that it's mine\n[01:29.280]I know that it's mine\n[01:34.170]I know that it's mine\n[01:41.500]I know that it's mine\n[01:51.230]I know that it's mine\n[01:56.160]I know that it's mine\n[02:02.970]Facing the change\n[02:05.320]But it’s still tough to see\n[02:07.900]At first I fought it all\n[02:10.900]I was so mean\n[02:12.900]I’m still unsure\n[02:15.100]How it’s supposed to be\n[02:17.470]But digging everyday now by the skin of my teeth\n[02:22.070]Until I learn\n[02:24.620]I’m holding on to all the pieces of my heart’s debris\n[02:29.330]Till it’s time\n[02:32.480]I’ll… I’ll pull it together and fix myself eventually\n[02:39.010]I know it’s mine\n[02:41.420]I found gold in the wreckage\n[02:43.720]Put it on a necklace\n[02:46.200]Keepin’ it cause I-I-I, I know that it’s mine\n[02:50.970]I wear it like a message\n[02:53.400]So I don’t forget it\n[02:55.960]Keepin’ it cause I-I-I, I know that it’s mine\n[03:03.960]I know that it’s mine\n[03:13.610]I know that it’s mine\n[03:23.330]I know that it’s mine\n[03:33.070]I know that it’s mine\n"},"klyric":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"tlyric":{"version":16,"lyric":"[00:21.300]当我堕落的时候\n[00:23.570]我被桎梏在这无形的悲伤里 喘不过气\n[00:26.280]曾经为此放弃一切 孤注一掷\n[00:28.700]在我缓缓坠向地面时\n[00:33.420]眼睁睁看着生命从我眼前溜走\n[00:35.760]我迷失了自己 如堕烟海\n[00:38.200]在我失去一切之前\n[00:40.860]我要勇敢地去把这一切拿回来\n[00:42.740]咬紧牙关 握紧我那支离破碎的心\n[00:47.670]直到最后一刻\n[00:50.670]我会将它一一拼凑 最后不药而愈\n[00:57.200]因为我知道这是属于我的\n[00:59.720]我在残垣断壁间拾到闪亮的金子\n[01:01.920]将它做成一串项链\n[01:04.320]好好地保管它 因为我知道这是属于我的\n[01:09.100]这是我存在的痕迹\n[01:11.670]所以我永不会忘记它\n[01:14.140]我会好好地保管它 因为我知道这是属于我的\n[01:19.700]我知道这是属于我的\n[01:24.480]我知道这是属于我的\n[01:29.280]我知道这是属于我的\n[01:34.170]我知道这是属于我的\n[01:41.500]我知道这是属于我的\n[01:51.230]我知道这是属于我的\n[01:56.160]我知道这是属于我的\n[02:02.970]面对朝云暮雨的日子\n[02:05.320]让人很难去看清事物的本质\n[02:07.900]最初我盲目地抵抗一切\n[02:10.900]那时的我太刻薄了\n[02:12.900]直到现在我也不确定\n[02:15.100]事情本应该是什么样子\n[02:17.470]但现在的我每一件事都会切身去寻找 去体会\n[02:22.070]直到我领悟\n[02:24.620]咬紧牙关 握紧我那支离破碎的心\n[02:29.330]直到最后一刻\n[02:32.480]我会将它一一拼凑 最后不药而愈\n[02:39.010]因为我知道这是属于我的\n[02:41.420]我在残垣断壁间拾到闪亮的金子\n[02:43.720]将它做成一串项链\n[02:46.200]好好地保管它 因为我知道这是属于我的\n[02:50.970]这是我存在的痕迹\n[02:53.400]所以我永远不会忘记它\n[02:55.960]我会好好地保管它 因为我知道这是属于我的\n[03:03.960]我知道这是属于我的\n[03:13.610]我知道这是属于我的\n[03:23.330]我知道这是属于我的\n[03:33.070]我知道这是属于我的"},"romalrc":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"code":200}